init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: One day when he was taken out for some fresh air, the alien is attacked by one of the other kids.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Every person on Earth was asked to help him find Matt Damon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He looked up in the sky and saw an alien ship.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He pulled a rocket launcher from his backpack and shot the ship out of the sky.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: People around the world were very happy and they were able to find him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien had finally realised that taking Matt Damon away from Earth was a mistake and he took him back and left.
